{"tid":1419811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"好多人係覺得我地慘所以支持我地","createTime":"2019-08-06T02:41:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T01:04:45.000Z","uid":854,"like":268,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"42734cd7cd1826d9891b1e04757727a541a6fd14","tid":1419811,"uid":854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:41:08.000Z","msg":"我地做緊嘅事當然係為公義為自由為本來應有嘅人權而做<br />\n<br />\n但呢啲概念並唔係每個路人都理解得咁清楚，<br />\n好多人唔明爭取自由，必須付出代價。<br />\n好多人見我地俾黑警打，不公平對待，覺得心痛因而支援我地。<br />\n呢個印象我地唔能夠失去。<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><br />\n<em><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">政府告訴我們，和平示威沒有用的。<br />\n行動升級是沒有選擇中的選擇。<br />\n暴力唔係目的，而係手段。<br />\n[/size=4]</em></span><br />\n呢三句我相信大部份連登仔都明，但係啲跟得唔貼嘅人未必明。<br />\n單睇一兩個放火畫面，個觀感自然唔會好睇，你好難叫一個人指住放火張圖向大眾大聲講我全力支持佢地放火！<br />\n<strong>[size=5]<span style=\"color: red;\">點解？</span></span></strong>因為你腦海好難直接將到我地嘅訴求/慘況同放火嘅動作聯想埋一齊。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">所以！</span></strong></span><br />\n在下有個提議，我地必須係前線都有<strong><ins>公關部</ins></strong>：<br />\n你地記唔記得呢位媽媽<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rTkj3su.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrTkj3su.png&h=aff0c9ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢嘅心底話令人動容<br />\n(當然我知道佢係真心，亦好感動）<br />\n我想講嘅係，我地需要做到類似嘅畫面！<br />\n人係直觀嘅生物，見火就驚，見人喊就覺得唔開心。<br />\n接下落嚟，無可避免會有更多火魔法。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">因此！</span></span></strong>我地必須用感人熱淚嘅畫面去沖淡火光。<br />\n<br />\n我懇請前線/和理非，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />請係鏡頭前，動之於情：控說我地嘅慘況、重覆五大訴求、唔好再傷害平民、唔好再擁護政府、政府都係想害你地etc. <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不停叫喊「政府呀！點解要咁對我地！點解咁對我地同警察！每個人都等緊政府回應五大訴求，回應咗就冇人再受傷！點解你咩都唔做！點解推香港人去死！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">唔好放棄行動，唔好放棄思考！<br />\nBe water and be humble!</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"c205a1fc42382efc24586c58945062f280a3013d","tid":1419811,"uid":854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:41:19.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"861a05ee70695c932b5387e2bf99d8313ac8c322","tid":1419811,"uid":854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:41:29.000Z","msg":"五大訴求"},{"pid":"fd2d36a5de464bc05781ca7b1d73af75932ac1fc","tid":1419811,"uid":854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:41:42.000Z","msg":"缺一不可"},{"pid":"41e13e477fa60c27e11f63ef6e292b0b99634fa3","tid":1419811,"uid":854,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:42:08.000Z","msg":"係咪自推十連會入黑洞"},{"pid":"bb30355cae1b862ad79027f480aaf3cf505b7921","tid":1419811,"uid":854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:42:38.000Z","msg":"認同請分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f24488693c91375cd2c5922ab98b385ce04a8c36","tid":1419811,"uid":854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:42:52.000Z","msg":"好人一生平安"},{"pid":"f2244ee741ed225cab6f7537d6aef0e27c1f6d96","tid":1419811,"uid":854,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:43:17.000Z","msg":"Btw 各位手足對市民禮貌啲呀"},{"pid":"538910d0d88ba02fce23c0906ed28b65d70e1cd6","tid":1419811,"uid":854,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:43:48.000Z","msg":"同埋做好保護自己個樣嘅措施"},{"pid":"5deb08d3aa3f73c7f4975679340708dc6fe87cd2","tid":1419811,"uid":854,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:44:16.000Z","msg":"求人唔好影 不如求己"},{"pid":"8feebc0ee35d429066087d8b2c98b198a19a2ed3","tid":1419811,"uid":854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:45:16.000Z","msg":"有冇手足幫手推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好驚冇左左post"},{"pid":"760fb4dc68b661d25bf55e533f1804ba82ceafbb","tid":1419811,"uid":854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:51:09.000Z","msg":"幫手推下呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5f25141620dc2d4909ed587431b75811990bcc5","tid":1419811,"uid":854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:51:26.000Z","msg":"多謝正評嘅巴打"},{"pid":"fc6b68e7378b65f228805c023446a805f29ca9fb","tid":1419811,"uid":854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:51:52.000Z","msg":"之前又話自推都上到熱門嘅？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68ab782c85ebf83197b36e20c0a44c5876624a8a","tid":1419811,"uid":186602,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fc6b68e7378b65f228805c023446a805f29ca9fb","tid":1419811,"uid":854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:51:52.000Z","msg":"之前又話自推都上到熱門嘅？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:53:44.000Z","msg":"講得好啱<br />\n<br />\n心理戰係最緊要"},{"pid":"78784c640e1351d6dd802d6e7d2acd268a42d2b6","tid":1419811,"uid":154486,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:54:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>機場呀</strong></span><br />\n1. 香港旅遊業春袋<br />\n2. 有冷氣<br />\n3. 已經有巴絲係度<br />\n4. 已經罷緊工<br />\n5. 林鄭好驚提機場<br />\n6. 機場cancel已上國際頭版<br />\n7. 機場特警係速龍，要佢地分飾兩角，姐係壯士斷臂<br />\n8. 唔會係室內開槍、放Tear Gas<br />\n9. 如果黑警封路 = 助攻<br />\n10. 最佳國際文宣機會"},{"